==English==
===Adjective===
'''lazy''' (''[[comparative]]'' '''lazier''', ''[[superlative]]'' '''laziest''')

#Unwilling to do work or make an effort.
#:''Get out of bed, you lazy lout!''
#Of an eye, [[squint]]ing because of a weakness of the eye [[muscle]]s.

